, 560px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>Homeschooler Appreciation<\/h2>\n<p>We&#8217;re wrapping up National Teacher Appreciation Week with something special for our homeschool educators! Friday (5\/8), we are giving out a $10.00 Gottwals Books GIFT CARD to our homeschool teachers. Must present some type of validation you are a homeschool teacher before picking up your gift card.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-5606\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/HomeschoolerAppreciation-600x305.jpg\" alt=\"HomeschoolerAppreciation\" width=\"600\" height=\"305\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>Kids&#8217; Corner All Summer Long!<\/h2>\n<p>Get your calendars ready because Kids&#8217; Corner will launch again the first week in June! We&#8217;ll have special guests, books, snacks, and prizes. We&#8217;ll be posting more information throughout May.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-5607\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/kids-corner--450x600.jpg\" alt=\"kids-corner-\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/kids-corner-.jpg 450w, https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/kids-corner--117x156.jpg 117w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>Author Feature: Nora Roberts &amp; J.D. Robb<\/h2>\n<p>Nora Roberts, author of just around 209 romance novels and the first author to be inducted in the Romance Writers of America Hall of Fame, is a reliable favorite of our customers. Classic and contemporary romance not quite your thing? Roberts also has a romantic suspense series under her pseudonym, J.D. Robb.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5605\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/gb-may7-newslettergraphic-2.jpg\" alt=\"gb-may7-newslettergraphic-2\" width=\"560\" height=\"284\" \/><\/p>\n<h2>Toy Feature<\/h2>\n<p>Melissa &amp; Doug&#8217;s chunky puzzles are the perfect size for little hands and are very versatile. The pieces fit in their slots and can stand upright. Like most other Melissa &amp; Doug products, you can create learning exercises for your child by lining up the pieces and counting them together, naming the colors on the puzzle, and identifying the insects. You can place the pieces around the room and go on a bug hunt, or use the pieces to create a story. With you, your child, and Melissa &amp; Doug working together, the fun never has to end!<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5609\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/Chunky-Puzzles.jpg\" alt=\"Chunky-Puzzles\" width=\"500\" height=\"377\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/Chunky-Puzzles.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/Chunky-Puzzles-207x156.jpg 207w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Friday, May 8, we are giving out a $10.00 Gottwals Books GIFT CARD to our homeschool teachers!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v18.1 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Friday, May 8, we are giving out a $10.00 Gottwals Books GIFT CARD to our homeschool teachers!\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.gottwalsbooks.com\/news\/new-store-sneak-peek-homeschoolers\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"New Store Sneak Peek + Homeschoolers! | Gottwals Books\" \/>\n<meta property